Title: Galveston Bay (468)

Author: U. S. Coast and Geodetic Survey

Date: 1951

Medium: Chromolithograph

Condition: Very Good - age toning, foxing, wear along issued folds, contemporary pencil annotations

Inches: 29 x 22 [Paper]

Centimeters: 73.66 x 55.88 [Paper]

World Aeronautical Chart Sheet 468 showing the Gulf Coast of Texas stretching from Matagorda Bay to Lake Borgne in Louisiana.
